<%
  var pageTitle   = 'Wealth — Lizzyland';
  var pageDesc    = 'Create your legacy. Build something beautiful that fits your brain and your life.';
  var currentPage = 'space';
%>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

<style>
  /* ── Hero — same proportions as shop ── */
  .ll-space-hero {
    position: relative; min-height: 280px;
    display: flex; align-items: flex-end;
    overflow: hidden; background: var(--warm-dark);
  }
  .ll-space-hero-img {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover; object-position: center 40%;
  }
  .ll-space-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to top,
      rgba(45,27,14,0.85) 0%,
      rgba(92,61,30,0.4) 55%,
      rgba(200,149,42,0.08) 100%
    );
  }
  .ll-space-hero-inner {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%; padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
  }
  .ll-space-hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em; opacity: 0.8; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .ll-space-hero-inner h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem,5vw,3.2rem);
    color: var(--white); margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }
  .ll-space-hero-inner p {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Intro ── */
  .ll-space-intro {
    background: var(--sand-light); padding: 4.5rem 2rem; text-align: center;
  }
  .ll-space-intro-inner { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .ll-space-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .ll-space-intro h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem,3.5vw,2.6rem);
    color: var(--warm-dark); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .ll-space-lead {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text-soft); line-height: 1.85;
  }

  /* ── Dream Finder / Wizard ── */
  .ll-dream-finder {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean) 0%, #0d6b5e 100%);
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }
  .ll-dream-finder-inner { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .ll-dream-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em; opacity: 0.8; margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .ll-dream-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.8rem);
    color: var(--white); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .ll-dream-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .ll-dream-cta-row { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .ll-dream-cta {
    display: inline-block; padding: 0.85rem 2.25rem;
    background: var(--gold); color: var(--warm-dark);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl); font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.25s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(200,149,42,0.3);
  }
  .ll-dream-cta:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .ll-dream-skip {
    display: inline-block; padding: 0.85rem 2.25rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl); color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.25s;
  }
  .ll-dream-skip:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18); }
  .ll-dream-note {
    font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    margin-top: 1.5rem; font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── Three web spaces ── */
  .ll-spaces {
    background: var(--cream); padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }
  .ll-spaces-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .ll-spaces-heading { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .ll-spaces-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .ll-spaces-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem,3.5vw,2.4rem);
    color: var(--warm-dark); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .ll-spaces-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .ll-spaces-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1.75rem;
  }
  .ll-space-card {
    background: var(--white); border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border: 1.5px solid var(--sand-deep);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem; transition: all 0.3s; position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ll-space-card::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ocean), var(--gold));
  }
  .ll-space-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }
  .ll-space-card-badge {
    display: inline-block; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    background: var(--ocean-pale); color: var(--ocean);
    font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl); margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .ll-space-card-badge.featured {
    background: rgba(200,149,42,0.12); color: var(--gold);
  }
  .ll-space-card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600; color: var(--warm-dark); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .ll-space-card-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-soft);
    line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .ll-space-price {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ocean); line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .ll-space-price-note {
    font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .ll-space-features {
    list-style: none; margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }
  .ll-space-features li {
    font-size: 0.87rem; color: var(--text-soft);
    padding: 0.35rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sand-deep);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .ll-space-features li::before { content: '✦'; color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.6rem; }
  .ll-space-cta {
    display: block; text-align: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--ocean); color: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl); font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .ll-space-cta:hover { background: var(--gold); color: var(--white); }

  /* ── How it works ── */
  .ll-how-it-works {
    background: var(--sand); padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }
  .ll-how-inner { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .ll-how-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem,3.5vw,2.4rem);
    color: var(--warm-dark); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .ll-how-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .ll-steps-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 2rem;
  }
  .ll-step-card {
    background: var(--white); border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem; position: relative;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--gold);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  .ll-step-number {
    position: absolute; top: 0.75rem; right: 1.25rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); opacity: 0.15; line-height: 1;
  }
  .ll-step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600; color: var(--warm-dark); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .ll-step-desc { color: var(--text-soft); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; }

  /* ── Coaching ── */
  .ll-coaching {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--warm-dark) 0%, #3d2510 100%);
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }
  .ll-coaching-inner {
    max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;
  }
  .ll-coaching-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em; opacity: 0.8; margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .ll-coaching-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.8rem); font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .ll-coaching-desc {
    font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(245,230,200,0.65);
    line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic; font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .ll-coaching-cta {
    display: inline-block; padding: 0.85rem 2.5rem;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(200,149,42,0.6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl); color: var(--gold-light);
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.92rem; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.25s;
  }
  .ll-coaching-cta:hover { background: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--warm-dark); }

  /* ── Back to doors ── */
  .ll-back-to-doors { padding: 2.5rem 2rem; background: var(--sand-light); }
  .ll-back-inner { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .ll-back-label { font-size: 0.72rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .ll-back-links { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .ll-back-link {
    display: inline-block; padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 50px; background: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid var(--sand-deep); color: var(--text-soft);
    font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.85rem; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .ll-back-link:hover { border-color: var(--ocean); color: var(--ocean); }
  .ll-back-home { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
  .ll-back-home:hover { background: var(--gold); color: var(--white); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .ll-spaces-grid, .ll-steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }
  }
</style>

  <!-- ══ HERO ══ -->
  <section class="ll-space-hero">
    <img src="/images/space-banner.jpg" alt="Wealth" class="ll-space-hero-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
    <div class="ll-space-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="ll-space-hero-inner">
      <div class="ll-space-hero-eyebrow">✦ Door Two · Wealth Coaching ✦</div>
      <h1>Create Your Legacy</h1>
      <p>Leave your mark.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ INTRO ══ -->
  <section class="ll-space-intro">
    <div class="ll-space-intro-inner">
      <div class="ll-space-eyebrow">Ready to scale your dreams?</div>
      <h2>Step into the lifestyle you desire.<br>It's easier than you think.</h2>
      <p class="ll-space-lead">
        Most people don't know what they actually want — only what they think they want.
        The gap between those two things is where everything changes.
        Let's find out what your beautiful future actually looks like.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ DREAM FINDER ══ -->
  <section class="ll-dream-finder">
    <div class="ll-dream-finder-inner">
      <div class="ll-dream-eyebrow">✦ The Dream Finder ✦</div>
      <h2 class="ll-dream-title">Not sure where to start?</h2>
      <p class="ll-dream-sub">
        A few simple questions. Your life's direction as the answer.
        I help people find their way to what they actually want —
        and then I help them build it.
      </p>
      <div class="ll-dream-cta-row">
        <a href="#" class="ll-dream-cta">Find My Direction →</a>
        <a href="#spaces" class="ll-dream-skip">I already know what I want</a>
      </div>
      <p class="ll-dream-note">The quiz takes about 3 minutes. No email required to start.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ THREE WEB SPACES ══ -->
  <section class="ll-spaces" id="spaces">
    <div class="ll-spaces-inner">
      <div class="ll-spaces-heading">
        <div class="ll-spaces-eyebrow">Your Internet Space</div>
        <h2 class="ll-spaces-title">Three ways to show up online.</h2>
        <p class="ll-spaces-sub">Done-for-you. Installed. Ready. Yours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ll-spaces-grid">

        <div class="ll-space-card">
          <span class="ll-space-card-badge">Starter</span>
          <div class="ll-space-card-title">The Calling Card</div>
          <div class="ll-space-card-desc">A beautiful one-page presence. Your story, your offer, your contact — nothing more. Perfect if you just need to exist online with dignity.</div>
          <div class="ll-space-price">$99</div>
          <div class="ll-space-price-note">once-off setup · hosting included year 1</div>
          <ul class="ll-space-features">
            <li>Single page — beautifully designed</li>
            <li>Your domain connected</li>
            <li>Contact form or booking link</li>
            <li>Mobile-perfect</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="mailto:hello@lizzyland.xyz" class="ll-space-cta">Get Started →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="ll-space-card">
          <span class="ll-space-card-badge featured">Most Popular</span>
          <div class="ll-space-card-title">The Full House</div>
          <div class="ll-space-card-desc">A proper multi-page website. Home, about, services, shop or blog — whatever your business needs. Done properly, from the beginning.</div>
          <div class="ll-space-price">$199</div>
          <div class="ll-space-price-note">once-off setup · hosting included year 1</div>
          <ul class="ll-space-features">
            <li>Up to 6 pages</li>
            <li>Your domain connected</li>
            <li>Shop or booking system</li>
            <li>Blog or portfolio ready</li>
            <li>You control everything</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="mailto:hello@lizzyland.xyz" class="ll-space-cta">Get Started →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="ll-space-card">
          <span class="ll-space-card-badge">Custom</span>
          <div class="ll-space-card-title">The Bespoke</div>
          <div class="ll-space-card-desc">You have something specific in mind. A marketplace, a membership, a complex shop, a booking platform. Let's talk about what you actually need.</div>
          <div class="ll-space-price">Let's talk</div>
          <div class="ll-space-price-note">custom quote · built around you</div>
          <ul class="ll-space-features">
            <li>Anything is possible</li>
            <li>Scoped to your needs</li>
            <li>Ongoing support available</li>
            <li>You own everything</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="mailto:hello@lizzyland.xyz" class="ll-space-cta">Have a Chat →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ HOW IT WORKS ══ -->
  <section class="ll-how-it-works">
    <div class="ll-how-inner">
      <h2 class="ll-how-title">How it works</h2>
      <p class="ll-how-sub">Three steps. That's it.</p>
      <div class="ll-steps-grid">
        <div class="ll-step-card">
          <div class="ll-step-number">01</div>
          <div class="ll-step-title">Tell me what you need</div>
          <p class="ll-step-desc">We have a conversation — email, voice note, whatever works for you. You don't need to know the technical words. Just tell me what you want your life to look like.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ll-step-card">
          <div class="ll-step-number">02</div>
          <div class="ll-step-title">I build and launch it</div>
          <p class="ll-step-desc">I handle everything. Design, setup, hosting, domain, testing. You'll see it before it goes live and we'll tweak until it's exactly right.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ll-step-card">
          <div class="ll-step-number">03</div>
          <div class="ll-step-title">You take the wheel</div>
          <p class="ll-step-desc">It's yours. I hand it over with a guide that actually makes sense. And I'm here when you need me — without the hourly bill anxiety.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ PERSONAL COACHING ══ -->
  <section class="ll-coaching">
    <div class="ll-coaching-inner">
      <div class="ll-coaching-eyebrow">✦ Not sure a website is the answer? ✦</div>
      <h2 class="ll-coaching-title">Sometimes the internet isn't the solution.<br>Sometimes it's a conversation.</h2>
      <p class="ll-coaching-desc">
        I'm a life coach as much as I am a web builder. If you're stuck — not sure which direction, not sure what you actually want to build, not sure how to get from here to there — let's talk. No agenda. Just clarity.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@lizzyland.xyz" class="ll-coaching-cta">Book a Conversation →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ EXPLORE OTHER DOORS ══ -->
  <section class="ll-back-to-doors">
    <div class="ll-back-inner">
      <p class="ll-back-label">Explore the other doors</p>
      <div class="ll-back-links">
        <a href="/health" class="ll-back-link">Health</a>
        <a href="/shop"   class="ll-back-link">Happiness</a>
        <a href="/"       class="ll-back-link ll-back-home">← Lizzyland</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="ll-divider">✦ · ✦ · ✦</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
